## Project Overview

This project demonstrates the deployment of a secure, publicly accessible web server on AWS. It covers VPC networking, EC2 provisioning, Linux administration, Nginx configuration, and IAM best practices.

-----

## Architecture

```
Internet Users
      |
Internet Gateway
      |
  Route Table  (0.0.0.0/0 → IGW)
      |
 Public Subnet  10.0.1.0/24
      |
 Security Group  (ports 22, 80, 443)
      |
  EC2 Instance  (Ubuntu, t2.micro)
      |
    Nginx  → Personal Portfolio Page
```

-----

